# Portfolio Website (React + Chakra UI)

A **responsive, Figma-driven portfolio website** built with **React**, **CSS Modules**, and **Chakra UI**, focused on clean layout architecture, consistent alignment, and mobile-first responsiveness.

***

## вњЁ Key Highlights

- **Single content rail system** for consistent alignment across all sections
- **Responsive navbar** вЂ” desktop grid nav, mobile hamburger with full-screen overlay
- **Hero section** вЂ” 2-column grid, layered visuals, Figma-matched typography
- **Quote section** вЂ” CSS Grid 3-row layout, author box seamlessly merged bottom-right
- **Chakra UI** adopted from Projects onwards вЂ” responsive props, SimpleGrid, Flex, Box
- **No horizontal scroll** вЂ” fixed widths overridden on mobile, absolute elements safely constrained

***

## рџ§± Layout System

```css
.content-rail {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1024px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
```

